# Estofmania

- Marketing site for an upholstery / estofos business (pt-PT).
- App lives in `site/` when scaffolded: Vite + React + TS + Tailwind v4 + `motion` + lucide-react.
- **Always** follow `design-system/estofmania/MASTER.md` for colors, fonts, and layout pattern.
- Use skills: `ui-ux-pro-max`, `estofmania-web`, `web-production`.
- Copy in European Portuguese. No emoji icons — SVG only.
- Before “done”: responsive check, a11y, SEO meta, browser preview via MCP.
